data.description: NEW NICE PRICE! Presenting the jewel of Princess Jeanne! This Originally Owned, Care-Fully Remodeled, Corner Lot home has Tons of Updates: Roof, Stucco, Flooring, Paint, Tankless Water Heater, Electrical, Kitchen Countertops & Ebony Butcher Block Island, bathroom Bluetooth speakers (all 2023). Newer evaporative cooler, windows, appliances. Entertain guests w/ the Beautiful Open Floorplan & Kitchen! Come & go through Private Entrances in 2 of the 4 bedrooms! Enjoy Mountain Views from the private walk out deck of your en-suite! Custom Iron Work throughout including the Backyard Access gates makes this home a unique Work of Art - See Docs for more Details! Located around the corner from Jeanne Bellamah Park & Community Center, minutes from I-40, Shopping, Foothills! Must see to believe
